</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The output is designed to verify the correct mirror mounting position. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> The test print contains 3 CMYK blocks printed in a 2 pass print mode. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-793B904A-0451-40A2-891B-9F1DE9C7A599" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-0EA5F197-8984-4841-9D85-CA0197A17876-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-0EA5F197-8984-4841-9D85-CA0197A17876-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Specification: 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Within the printed patches, a gloss and matte area must be visible. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">If not: check if the FLXfinish<sup class="+ topic/ph hi-d/sup ">+</sup> mirror is installed. 
</p></li></ul><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Within the patches 2 small lines are printed to illustrate the correct working range. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">If the matte-gloss transition is in between the 2 small lines the mirror is correctly installed. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">If not, adjustment of the FLXfinish<sup class="+ topic/ph hi-d/sup ">+</sup> mirror 
</p></li></ul></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-780E6E2B-05D8-4B9F-BB79-59B9367055BD" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-C3940AE3-DAF4-4382-B801-5EB6C83B24EE-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-C3940AE3-DAF4-4382-B801-5EB6C83B24EE-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-1F897B6A-3B52-4EA1-AC18-9626A9B429D4.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Adjustment</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
